The Teacher parade is tomorrow at 12:00. We don't have a route because we don't want anyone leaving their yard... We will drive around honking and yelling; you will be able to hear us, I'm sure. We are going to adhere to all the safety protocols, so we will be waving and staying hi only.
Teachers will not be getting out of their car. Students should remain in their yards practicing social distancing to remain safe. I think it is going to be fun. Hope to see you then.
